Whereas the Department of Defense claims a 24-percent
			 surplus in domestic military infrastructure and has requested domestic Base
			 Realignment and Closure (BRAC) rounds in 2015 and 2017;

Whereas the Government Accountability Office concluded in
			 a 2007 study that the 2005 BRAC round was the most complex and costliest
